  <summary>3/20/1997--Introduced.
Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude from gain the sale of a life estate or a remainder interest in a principal residence by a person eligible for the one-time "55 years or older" exclusion of gain from the sale of such residence. Stipulates that such provision shall not apply to related party sales.</summary>
